### SoundList API — Exemplos de requisições
### Compatível com IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client e VS Code REST Client
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

# =============================================================================
# PLAYLISTS
# =============================================================================

### [1] Criar uma nova playlist (POST) → espera 201 Created
POST http://localhost:8080/api/playlists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Minha Playlist Rock",
  "description": "Seleção pessoal de rock"
}


### [2] Criar playlist sem nome (POST) → espera 400 Bad Request (validação)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/playlists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "Sem nome"
}

---

### [3] Listar todas as playlists — página 0, 5 por página (GET) → 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlists?size=20

---

### [4] Buscar playlist por id (GET) → 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlists/1

---

### [5] Buscar playlist inexistente (GET) → 404 Not Found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlists/999

---

### [6] Atualizar playlist (PUT) → 200 OK
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/playlists/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rock Clássico Atualizado",
  "description": "Descrição atualizada"
}

---

### [7] Deletar playlist e suas músicas em cascata (DELETE) → 204 No Content
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/playlists/2

---

# =============================================================================
# MÚSICAS
# =============================================================================

### [8] Adicionar música a uma playlist (POST) → 201 Created
POST http://localhost:8080/api/musics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Back in Black",
  "artist": "AC/DC",
  "genre": "Hard Rock",
  "duration": 255,
  "playlistId": 1
}

---

### [9] Música com playlist inexistente (POST) → 404 Not Found
POST http://localhost:8080/api/musics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Orphan Song",
  "artist": "Nobody",
  "genre": "Pop",
  "duration": 180,
  "playlistId": 999
}

---

### [10] Música com validações inválidas (POST) → 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/musics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "artist": "",
  "duration": -10,
  "playlistId": null
}

---

### [11] Listar músicas paginadas (GET) → 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/musics?size=20

---

### [12] Buscar música por id (GET) → 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/musics/1

---

### [13] Buscar música inexistente (GET) → 404 Not Found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/musics/9999

---

### [14] Atualizar música (PUT) → 200 OK
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/musics/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bohemian Rhapsody (Remaster)",
  "artist": "Queen",
  "genre": "Rock / Opera",
  "duration": 360,
  "playlistId": 1
}

---

### [15] Deletar música (DELETE) → 204 No Content
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/musics/9

---

